{
  "stem": "22447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you see, you either pay the premium to learn a trade or you didn't pay the premium and you didn't get paid.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the-- and then after six months, I got a shilling a week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But occasionally, if you delivered a suit, you might get a tip, sixpence or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But other than that-- but it taught you a good trade, you see?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can always go and earn your money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because you-- even if you did, you knew you wasn't going to get anywhere unless you had a sponsor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, if you had someone to pay for you to go to university or something, you wasn't going to get anywhere so you didn't bother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, some people don't don't like-- like, being sponsored by other people, say, I don't want anyone to give me anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want to get there but the sweat of my own brow, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So know one can ever point the finger at you and say, well, if it wasn't for me, you wouldn't be where you are.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you'd-- you'd go sometimes to a meeting, a political meeting or something, that-- of course, we-- not because you was politically minded, it was some kind of entertainment, with the heckling.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're more just like professional hecklers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like an [LAUGHS] entertainment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So people would go to meetings or-- or they'd go dancing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or there'd be--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, conservative meetings or labor-party meetings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people go heckling all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it would be like a-- fun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, they didn't-- never let the speaker speak because they were always asking difficult questions and arguments and all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just to pass the time away, that's all.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
